{"tid":1565841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[和理非要進化]200萬人行街食飯創舉","createTime":"2019-09-13T10:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:27:58.000Z","uid":45788,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"78f6d9da210e3717b8c7aec5836df5b112937836","tid":1565841,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"依家民陣基本上係警犬嘅手段下基本上冇可能有不反對書<br />\n但我覺得作為一個香港人，係咪要係人地濫用公權力嘅底下屈服？<br />\n我相信經歷咗三個月嘅香港人心中有答案<br />\n5大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n呢d口號唔係在心中，或者係商場喊下就可以實現<br />\n818我地做到流水式集會<br />\n<br />\n去到依家一個樽頸位，我相信大家可以做到200萬人自發行街食飯嘅創舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個禮拜適逢人權法案<br />\n希望大家出嚟食飯行街<br />\n再造一次百萬人冇領導下嘅行街<br />\n以行動抗議警暴<br />\n以行動守護自由<br />\n同希望呢次係和理非為主<br />\n<br />\n大家還記得勇武&gt;&gt;&gt;和理非&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;勇武patten?<br />\n<br />\n915差乜<br />\n差你出哦咋<br />\n<br />\n用行動證明，比世界睇清楚<br />\n我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n好冇？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffx77P1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fffx77P1.jpg&h=1dba5785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnYbP3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnYbP3o.jpg&h=927a3730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zgS4qBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzgS4qBN.jpg&h=18c8a49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1jKqBO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1jKqBO.jpg&h=4b603c93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d07ad163af878614b9c30206344769b8bc2f4fc","tid":1565841,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4d1dd1e37f4e81ebd0d9e4e156c96e7eb43dc5","tid":1565841,"uid":1003